Dan?

3
00:00:47,520 --> 00:00:50,159
What's wrong? You were swimming normally just now.

4
00:00:52,759 --> 00:00:53,880
I just...

5
00:00:55,679 --> 00:00:57,280
I just saw Trin.

6
00:00:57,359 --> 00:00:58,359
