13
00:01:23,239 --> 00:01:24,519
I think he's dead.

14
00:01:29,560 --> 00:01:31,760
He really had a hand in making the shadow stronger.

15
00:01:32,920 --> 00:01:34,760
I think it's related.

16
00:01:36,799 --> 00:01:38,680
