52
00:04:27,920 --> 00:04:29,199
- Number One! - Number One!

53
00:04:29,279 --> 00:04:30,279
- Number One! - Number One!

54
00:04:30,360 --> 00:04:31,959
Trin.

55
00:04:32,050 --> 00:04:33,050
