72
00:05:23,120 --> 00:05:24,240
Do not talk back!

73
00:05:24,319 --> 00:05:25,319
Yes, sir.

74
00:05:25,839 --> 00:05:26,959
Anyway,

75
00:05:27,050 --> 00:05:30,079
