00:06:37,600 --> 00:06:38,600
Two.

104
00:06:39,120 --> 00:06:40,160
One.

105
00:06:42,439 --> 00:06:44,279
If you want to call me over to have a word,

106
00:06:45,199 --> 00:06:48,439
